A lil summer beat to beat the heat 🔥 @tiarramonet spills the tea on her #hotgirlsummer makeup routine:
✨ Honey Dew Me Up Primer
✨ Total Controp Pro Drop Foundation in 'Mocha'
✨ Total Control Pro Drop Foundation Hue Shifter in 'Cool'
✨ Ultimate Shadow Palette in 'Utopia'
✨ Brow Glue
✨ Lift & Snatch Brow Tint Pen in 'Espresso'
✨ Shine Loud High Shine Lip Color in 'Rebel in Red' + 'Cash Flow'
Shop the look at nyxcosmetics.com • #nyxcosmetics #nyxprofessionalmakeup #crueltyfreebeauty
